data.description: Great opportunity!  Fabulous cul de sac location. Corner lot with nice brick entryway. Front yard recently landscaped. Originally a 5+3 but  the 2 downstairs bedrooms have been converted into 1 big bedroom(currently a 4+3). Spacious floor plan with a large living room with a fireplace and a bay window. Big eat in kitchen with a garden window to enjoy the mountain views. Family room with slider to the backyard. Inside laundry. Huge downstairs bedroom. Downstairs bath with tiled shower area and tile flooring.  Spacious master bedroom with a walk in closet and beautiful mountain views. Large secondary bedrooms upstairs with mountain views.  Big hall bathroom upstairs with lots of counter space. Interior features include scraped ceilings throughout, mirrored closet doors, ceiling fans and some dual pane windows. Private backyard with a pool, spa & covered patio with more great mountain views from the backyard. Newer roof.. Great opportunity!!
